cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with video prediction and unsupervised video representation learning. It also uses concepts from systems identification theory, which is related to control and robotics (cs.RO) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. Additionally, the use of a novel network architecture and learning approach suggests that it may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
